data.description:
Spacious Patio Home! If you want all 1st-Floor Living at a great price, don't miss this 2 Bedroom, 2 Full Bath home! 

You enter the large Living Room with 12' vaulted ceiling and gas fireplace which is open to the Dining Room and Kitchen area giving you plenty of room for family and friends! You'll notice an abundance of windows throughout the home allowing tons of natural light. The Kitchen has 2 nice sized pantry closets and higher end cabinetry with pull out shelving.  

Off the Kitchen in the rear of the home is a big Office Space that opens to the rear Patio with plenty of privacy for those nice summer evenings at home.  Between the Kitchen and 2-Car Garage is a nice Laundry/Mud Room. The Primary suite has 2 double closets and ensuite Full Bath with a full walk-in closet.  In the front portion of the home, you will find a Guest Bedroom and Full Bath.

The 2-Car Attached Garage has a big storage closet with heat & A/C to keep your stored items from extreme temperatures.  And there is a bunch of closet space, which you don't always find in a patio home!

Maintenance fee includes water, sewer, and trash pickup in addition to Master Insurance and external groundskeeping & maintenance (windows and doors are owner's responsibility). 

Rentals are prohibited.
